      <textAnnotation id="sid-B6B7FCD6-2A2E-413F-83DB-E1F031F6E287" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process Tower : OTC -Order to Cash
Process Group: O_Order Management
Process: O-060-070_Monitor Check Order Status


</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-759F5A6B-0A83-439E-AB3A-4ADB0C9DAF5A" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Customer contacts CBA to request a change</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-6B7BFCCA-A622-4E3C-95D2-19502896C59A" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/2bf0b2de046548f488f7d54621c5b176</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>EDI</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-3F1A9EA6-3AA5-4A7E-9988-22260C21864D" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/12e70e612dcb494bb9001cc0474e899a</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Web Order
 Management</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-2A71A35F-2889-494F-8F37-9C4B1C329220" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bottom="false" left="false" ref="text_name" right="false" top="true" valign="bottom" x="32.0" y="-9.0"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-8349F57F-3A61-476E-8422-E8B4E53E45CA" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-0012AAD6-A48F-4F0B-8EFE-14678E7C014A" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-542145C5-CF73-4534-BF2F-C64AE6B23727" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel align="right" bottom="false" left="true" ref="text_name" right="false" top="false" valign="middle" x="-7.0" y="29.0"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-5D7932BC-AE5C-4642-B010-D29FA6E56FB8" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1. Prior to sending change for approval, CBA checks if Sales Order Line item (SOLI) has a delivery note created &amp; where it is in processing. 
 2. If Customer persists approval is requested to concerned Manager
3) Approval discussion will also include if any charges need to be applied 
4) Assumption &gt; Upside in demand does not require approval.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-81337DAE-755B-4D8F-9DC9-F5A76424F82B" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1 - No changes can be made to Business Partner ID (Sold to and Ship to) if any SOLIs have DN/shipped
2 - CBA can manually add a new line (to split existing line item, add any chargeable services, new MMID...etc)
3.No increase to line item order QTY for all order types
4 - Changing line item category (e.g. TAN to TANN)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-D7CC5DE9-8AB4-487D-8F00-D465D27071AC" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-9D0ADE86-C09D-432B-A844-C0113CBB225C" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bottom="false" left="false" ref="text_name" right="false" top="true" valign="bottom" x="32.0" y="-9.0"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-3461C9AC-9A14-4987-88C8-14BF04C7D53E" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Example of changes:
1.Line Item Category
2. New Line Creation
3. Apply Holds or Flags
4. DNI flag and Update 
pricing condition 
5. Price Override
6. CPN Adjustment
7. Shipahead Window</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-0CC841DA-BFC9-4BBC-A275-C9F8B3EACB73" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel align="right" bottom="false" left="true" ref="text_name" right="false" top="false" valign="middle" x="-7.0" y="29.0"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP 
S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-0287E0CA-4354-4D40-8AA7-44D1762F3321" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>If approval is granted, continue to communicate decision with customer via email</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-68DDB4EB-4F6E-4EFE-8A12-A78A821B69AB" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Examples of Internal inquiry: - Exception case Plant code - Use tray MM instead of Box - MOQ need to be broken down - Max Delivery note size reached</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-B6A2E23A-96B3-47C4-99D9-739B0CD7BB54" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/f304934a2cda4988bf97484658f73148</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Dassian</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-221431A7-DCB0-4A82-857A-7C602083CD8A" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1- if QTY on SOLI is increased, then a new line item must be created for the increased QTY. 
2- Add a link to pricing flows (XOA3, Commercial invoice, pricing refresh)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-C51A9C21-6C8F-4959-9489-48EE86C06448" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>if QTY on SOLI is increased, then a new line item must be created for the increased QTY.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-7DC37B2E-F6C6-460A-8065-ED7CA4310D23" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1.Credit check will occur if changes are saved on a SO1 SOLI 
2.FSCM stands for financial supply chain management</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
